(4585, 131054, 'Maria EP', '歌詞 : \r\n\r\n1. Intro \r\n擊沈女孩是誰啊？\r\n\r\n2. Today is a Good Day to Die \r\n4 walls in this jail cell \r\nmouth’s shut i will never tell \r\neyes watching everywhere they see\r\n\r\nhere’s a knife cut your chords right now\r\ninnocence never spoke so loud\r\nnow clean your hands and you’ll be free\r\n\r\ni don’t know where we are going \r\nand i don’t have anything to get us by \r\nall i know is we’re all dying \r\nso let’s drink this poison til we fall asleep \r\n\r\nfree time to just waste time \r\nit was the perfect crime \r\nbut why aren’t we satisfied? \r\n\r\nshut your mouth, what have you got to lose?\r\npack up your things and don’t forget your shoes \r\ngone so fast like you would not believe\r\n\r\n2. 30分鐘\r\n請給我30分鐘\r\n讓我看你的笑容\r\n但你還要離開我\r\n我怎麼辦\r\n\r\n請給我30分鐘\r\n好像是你聽不懂\r\n讓我心一直跳動\r\n你知不知道？\r\n\r\ncigarettes and A.D.D \r\nwere always cool with me \r\n\r\nevery time that i fucked up \r\nit always comforts me \r\n\r\nwell can you pick me up\r\nbefore i fall asleep \r\ni don’t know what we’re doing \r\n\r\n4. 小澤瑪莉雅\r\n\r\nif looks could kill then sign me up \r\nand put me six feet under \r\nthe girl you’d never thought you’d be \r\n\r\nand while i gasped for air you’d smile while you caressed your hair \r\n\r\nthe things i’d do for you that no one could compare \r\nto how you looked at me and said i love you too\r\n\r\nthose deadly eyes \r\nand all those guys that you put six feet under \r\ni’m next in line why can’t you see \r\n\r\nthe way you play with my heart isn’t fair you never cared\r\n\r\n5. 99 Part 2\r\n三點99要關門了\r\n我們到7去買更多酒\r\n錢包空空但回家還夠\r\n你想去哪\r\n我想要回家\r\n\r\n我說你要去打個電話喔\r\n我的眼睛閉一下\r\n\r\n但是你已經打車回家\r\n那我一個人回家好了\r\n\r\n6. Oh No\r\nyou said that i was getting older \r\nyou said it don''t help that we ain''t getting any younger \r\n\r\noh no \r\n\r\nyou said that my life''s getting shorter \r\nyou said there''s point in trying to make it any longer\r\n\r\noh no\r\n\r\nHEY YO\r\n\r\n\r\n', '2012-06-08 00:00:00', 0, 2, 10, '